{"tid":2257323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國副總統彭斯助手染新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T06:17:35.000Z","uid":278587,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28b24ff5cf27f40df4aac6e5770290530263b6b6","tid":2257323,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=410397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410397&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=179f56f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410397&h=4dffd8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=410397</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國副總統彭斯的辦公室主任感染新型冠狀病毒，彭斯一名密切顧問也傳出確診。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯辦公室主任肖特新冠病毒檢測呈陽性，正接受隔離及追蹤密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道，跟彭斯非常密切的政治顧問奧布斯特也確診。彭斯的發言人表示，彭斯和太太的病毒檢測呈陰性，健康狀況良好，暫時無計劃改變競選行程。<br />\n<br />\n肖特是彭斯最親密的助手，按照美國疾控中心指引，彭斯屬於密切接觸者。"},{"pid":"49ff59dee9dd787125c6a72a9e63b4b838dc3f2a","tid":2257323,"uid":374180,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f953c579e6dd5dd9c61037ca8ecaa0c15539aab3","tid":2257323,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a9c255704a000bef6b60e0b4a8893ade97a8b6","tid":2257323,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}